name: Revenge of the 'Gator
overview: 'Gators galore! Eight scrolling screens - secret entrances to bonus areas - hungry 'Gators that unexpectedly swallow your ball and and move it to a new screen - all in a package you can slip into a pocket and take with you anywhere. You'd need a pinball machine the size of the Everglades to hold all this excitement! King of the Bayou or 'Gator bait - this pinball game's got all the options!
